          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "冷えた体には、温かいけんちん汁が一番だ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "お正月には、家族みんなでけんちん汁を囲んで食卓を共にする。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "わあ、けんちん汁だ！大根が柔らかくて美味しいね。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 3,
        "gloss": "black soybean sprouts fried in sesame seed oil wrapped in dried beancurd and stewed",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "特製の黒豆もやしを使った巻繊は、ここでしか味わえない逸品だ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "この地方の巻繊は、黒豆もやしを胡麻油で炒めてから煮込むのが特徴だ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "へえ、こんな巻繊もあるんだ。黒豆もやしの食感が楽しいね。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      }
